dcterms:description: A real data set of shell lengths of the white clam A. alba, composed of 675 individuals collected over seven sampling months and binned into 14 length classes. This dataset was used to test the reproducibility and precision of length-based methods.
dcterms:title: Abra alba

dcterms:description: A synthetic length-frequency data set created by selecting the first 12 months from the original synlfq5 data set in TropFishR, consisting of 36,711 individuals. This dataset was used to test the accuracy and reproducibility of ELEFAN-based fit methods.
dcterms:title: synlfq5b
